OL,7,FA survivor of the Manchester Arena
OL,8,Fbombing says disabled access in
OL,9,FManchester City Centre and the
OL,10,Fhospital where he receives regular
OL,11,Ftreatment, can be "exhausting" and
OL,12,F"tough".
OL,14,Fwho went to the concert after buying
OL,15,Ftickets for his daughter Eve, was the
OL,16,Fclosest person to the bomber to
OL,17,Fsurvive and was told five weeks after
OL,18,Fthe attack that he would never walk
OL,19,Fagain.
