OL,3,CArena bombing survivor user says
OL,4,Cdisabled access in Manchester is
OL,5,C'tough'
OL,7,F"You've got to look at everything
OL,8,Ftactfully. How i'm going to get up,
OL,9,Fhow i'm going to get down. It's
OL,10,Fexhausting."
OL,12,FHe added: "Let's get planners and
OL,13,Farchitects around the table and get
OL,14,Fthem to test all these (the roads)
OL,15,Fwith a wheelchair user or a disabled
OL,16,Fperson or a mother with a pram. I bet
OL,17,Fthey haven't.
