OL,7,FOne of Martin's favourite restaurants
OL,8,Fin Manchester City Centre Tattu, a
OL,9,Fcontemporary Chinese food and cocktail
OL,10,Fbar, does not have a lift which which
OL,11,Fposes a lot of challenges for
OL,12,Fwheelchair users.
OL,14,FHe said: "It's disappointing. I came
OL,15,Fin the opening two weeks, I think that
OL,16,Fwas in 2015 or 2016. We came several
OL,17,Ftimes before I was injured."
