OL,3,CArena bombing survivor user says
OL,4,Cdisabled access in Manchester is
OL,5,C'tough'
OL,7,F"There's laws to say I shouldn't get
OL,8,Fdiscriminated against because I'm in a
OL,9,Fwheelchair and it's busy every night,
OL,10,Fso you're not telling me that they
OL,11,Fcouldn't put a lift in."
OL,13,FSalford Royal Hospital is where
OL,14,FMartin's life was saved following the
OL,15,Farena bombing.
OL,17,FDue to building work on the hospital's
OL,18,Fmain site, the closest disabled car
OL,19,Fparking spaces are on a hill.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
