OL,3,CArena bombing survivor user says
OL,4,Cdisabled access in Manchester is
OL,5,C'tough'
OL,7,F"This hospital saved my life and it's
OL,8,Fgreat and I feel at home here, but
OL,9,Flooking up (the hill), you know I
OL,10,Fclimbed Kilimanjaro and I don't think
OL,11,FI was as out of breathe," he continued.
OL,13,F"It's really tough. Get the planners,
OL,14,Fget the local council to ask 'do you
OL,15,Fthink this is adequate? Right, you get
OL,16,Facross here in a wheelchair and up
OL,17,Fthere and i'll give you 5 minutes'.
OL,18,FThey won't be able to do it."
